---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy — Restoration Medical"
  description="How Restoration Medical collects, uses, and protects personal and health information."
>
  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="wrap-narrow prose reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="footer__fine">Last updated: June 2026 · Placeholder — review with legal counsel before launch.</p>

      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        Restoration Medical is a physician-led practice operating two divisions, Medical Aesthetics
        and Infusion Therapy. This policy covers personal information collected through this website
        and across both divisions.
      </p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Information you provide through our consult and contact forms (such as your name, email, and
        phone number), and limited technical information collected automatically to keep the site
        secure and working. Please do not submit sensitive medical details through website forms.
      </p>

      <h2>How we use it</h2>
      <p>
        To respond to your enquiry, arrange consultations, and operate the practice. We do not sell
        your personal information.
      </p>

      <h2>Health information</h2>
      <p>
        Personal health information collected in the course of care is handled in accordance with
        Ontario’s Personal Health Information Protection Act (PHIPA) and applicable professional
        obligations.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy can be directed to the practice via our
        <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .prose h2 {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .prose p {
      color: var(--graphite);
      max-width: var(--measure);
    }
  </style>
</Base>
